Camellias in a stone water basin at Honen-in, near the Philosopher’s Path.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
哲学の道の近くにある、法然院の蹲の椿。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Temples" /><category term="Flowers" /><summary type="html">Camellias in a stone water basin at Honen-in, near the Philosopher’s Path.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2103_A7R03131.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Ema・絵馬</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210310/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Ema・絵馬" /><published>2021-03-10T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-03-10T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/ema</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210310/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Emas are wood plaques for writing wishes at Shinto shrines. Most shrines have their own unique designs. These are at Shimogamo Jinja. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
絵馬は神社で願い事を書くための木の板です。 それぞれに独自のデザインがあります。 これは下鴨神社のです。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Shrines" /><summary type="html">Emas are wood plaques for writing wishes at Shinto shrines. Most shrines have their own unique designs. These are at Shimogamo Jinja.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2103_A7R03039.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Kamo Ohashi Bridge・賀茂大橋</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210309/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Kamo Ohashi Bridge・賀茂大橋" /><published>2021-03-09T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-03-09T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/kamo-ohashi</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210309/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Steel girders on the underside of the Kamo Ohashi Bridge make a graphic pattern. One of many bridges over the Kamo River, this is where Imadegawa Street crosses the river.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
賀茂大橋 の した 下 の はがね 鋼 が グラフィック もよう 模様 に なっています 。 今出川通が鴨川を渡るところです 。 
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Bridges" /><category term="Architecture" /><summary type="html">Steel girders on the underside of the Kamo Ohashi Bridge make a graphic pattern. One of many bridges over the Kamo River, this is where Imadegawa Street crosses the river. 賀茂大橋 の した 下 の はがね 鋼 が グラフィック もよう 模様 に なっています 。 今出川通が鴨川を渡るところです 。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2103_A7R03065.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Sakura at Seiryo-ji・清涼寺の桜</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210308/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Sakura at Seiryo-ji・清涼寺の桜" /><published>2021-03-08T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-03-08T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/seiryo-ji</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210308/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Early cherry blossoms at Seiryo-ji Temple in Arashiyama.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
嵐山の清凉寺の早桜。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Cherry Blossoms" /><category term="Temples" /><summary type="html">Early cherry blossoms at Seiryo-ji Temple in Arashiyama. 嵐山の清凉寺の早桜。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2103_A7R03010.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Sakura at Toji Temple・東寺の桜</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210307/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Sakura at Toji Temple・東寺の桜" /><published>2021-03-07T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-03-07T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/toji</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210307/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Cherry blossoms are starting to bloom in front of the Pagoda at Toji Temple. There was a moment of sun and blue sky to capture this image, on an otherwise cloudy day.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
東寺の五重塔の前に桜が咲き始めています。曇りの日でしたが、晴れ間があってこの撮影ができました。

&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Cherry Blossoms" /><category term="Temples" /><summary type="html">Cherry blossoms are starting to bloom in front of the Pagoda at Toji Temple. There was a moment of sun and blue sky to capture this image, on an otherwise cloudy day. 東寺の五重塔の前に桜が咲き始めています。曇りの日でしたが、晴れ間があってこの撮影ができました。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2103_A7R02985.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Peaceful Bamboo・平和な竹林</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210304/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Peaceful Bamboo・平和な竹林" /><published>2021-03-04T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-03-04T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/chikurin</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210304/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    A sunny afternoon in Arashiyama’s Bamboo Grove.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
嵐山の竹林で晴たの日の午後。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Bamboo Grove" /><summary type="html">A sunny afternoon in Arashiyama’s Bamboo Grove. 嵐山の竹林で晴たの日の午後。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2103_A7R02943.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Yodosuiro・淀水路</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210303/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Yodosuiro・淀水路" /><published>2021-03-03T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-03-03T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/sakura</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210303/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
    Thousands of Kawazu cherry blossoms in bloom, but this one called out to me.
&lt;/p&gt;



&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
何千本もの河津桜が咲いていますが、これは特に綺麗だと思いました。
&lt;/p&gt;

