&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kiyomizudera" /><category term="Architecture" /><summary type="html">Architectural details of Kiyomuzudera Temple, from a few weeks ago.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2102_A7R02099.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Ume at Jonangu・城南宮の梅花</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210301/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Ume at Jonangu・城南宮の梅花" /><published>2021-03-01T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-03-01T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/jonangu</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210301/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
